This directory is for project-specific (private) libraries.
PlatformIO compiles each library here into a static archive and links it into the executable.

Each library should live in its own subdirectory, e.g.:

  lib/
    SomeLib/
      src/
        SomeLib.cpp
        SomeLib.h

More info: https://docs.platformio.org/page/librarymanager/index.html
